### 狀態檢查
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### 建立報名 (成功案例)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "REST Client",
  "email": "rest@example.com",
  "phone": "0988777666",
  "password": "restrest",
  "confirmPassword": "restrest",
  "interests": ["全端", "後端"],
  "terms": true
}

### 測試：缺少必填欄位 (name)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rest@example.com",
  "phone": "0988777666",
  "password": "restrest",
  "confirmPassword": "restrest",
  "interests": ["全端"],
  "terms": true
}
# 預期：400 Bad Request, "name 為必填"

### 測試：手機格式錯誤
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Failed Phone",
  "email": "rest@example.com",
  "phone": "1234567890",
  "password": "restrest",
  "confirmPassword": "restrest",
  "interests": ["全端"],
  "terms": true
}
# 預期：400 Bad Request, "手機需為 09 開頭 10 碼"

### 測試：密碼與確認密碼不一致
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Failed Password",
  "email": "rest@example.com",
  "phone": "0911222333",
  "password": "passwordA",
  "confirmPassword": "passwordB",
  "interests": ["全端"],
  "terms": true
}
# 預期：400 Bad Request, "密碼與確認密碼不一致"

### 測試：未勾選服務條款
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No Terms",
  "email": "rest@example.com",
  "phone": "0911222333",
  "password": "passwordpassword",
  "confirmPassword": "passwordpassword",
  "interests": ["全端"]
  // "terms" 欄位遺失或為 false
}
# 預期：400 Bad Request, "請勾選服務條款"


